  <h2>Chicken Parmesan</h2>

  <p>The delicious italian dish can remind you of sunday night dinners and bring you back to your childhood</p>

  <h2>Ingrediants for sauce:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>1/2 large yellow onion to make 3/4 cup of grated onion</li>
    <li>1/4 cup olive oil</li>
    <li>2 medium garlic cloves, peeled and minced</li>
    <li>1 can crushed tomatoes</li>
    <li>1 teaspoon dried oregano</li>
    <li>pinch of red pepper flakes</li>
    <li>pinch of sugar</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Ingrediants for chicken:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>4 chicken breat cutlets</li>
    <li>Salt</li>
    <li>2 eggs</li>
    <li>1 cup breadcrumps</li>
    <li>1 cup parmesan cheese</li>
    <li>1/4 cup olive oil</li>
    <li>2 tbsp fresh basil leaves</li>
    <li>8 ounces mozzarella cheese, sliced</li>
